channel.title: High Road To Taos Scenic Byway on Roadsign Pictures
channel.description: Recent content in High Road To Taos Scenic Byway on Roadsign Pictures

item.title: End NM-76 North at NM-75
item.description: End NM-76 north at NM-75. Turn right on NM-76 north to continue on the High Road To Taos Scenic Byway.

item.title: End NM-503 East at NM-76
item.description: End NM-503 East at NM-76 in rural Rio Arriba County. NM-76 is the High Road To Taos Scenic Byway.

item.title: NM-503 East at CH-98
item.description: NM-503 East at CH-98 North. Use CH-98 north for Sanitario de Chimayo and Chimayo. Continue east on NM-503 for Cundiyo and Santa Cruz Lake. The High Road To Taos Scenic Byway turns left here.

item.title: US-84/US-285 North Approaching NM-503
item.description: US-84/US-285 North approaching NM-503 in Pojoaque. This is the beginning of the High Road To Taos Scenic Byway.
